Classification of metabolites based on ApoE class

A function was created to streamline the analysis of mulyiple (tidy tabular standardised) predictors and response. The function fit takes the arguments X = data frame of predictors and Y = response, fits a Logistic Regression, a Decision Tree and a (bagging) Random Forest. It subsequently creates a dataframe with the repeated 10-fold Cross-Validation(CV) model performance evaluation metrics and plots the ROC curves.
